<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Mikey</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-29 06:28:46</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>My buddies and I were fighting on level 3 of befallen when we fought the theurgamist(spelling sucks).  We were able to obtain two gossimer robes, and the theurgamest robe.  Also, we got the dagger or marnak two or three times.  The first two times were really easy, 2 shamans and three warriors. We had two level 21, two level 20's, and a level 19. The second time we were fighting the Priest showed up to put a wrench in the works, but we iced him pretty fast.  The third time it was a little harder since we lost one our tanks cause he had to log.  I wouldnt even attempt to try and get down there unless you are at least lvl 18 in a group, or lvl 24 on your own, since most people are KOS to just about everything, and if one gets away, he brings four friends with him on the way back.</font></td></tr></table>
